<dec f='include/samba-4.0/libsmbclient.h' l='1763' type='int smbc_statvfs(char * url, struct statvfs * st)'/>
<doc f='include/samba-4.0/libsmbclient.h' l='1743'>/**@ingroup attribute
 * Get file system information for a specified path.
 *
 * @param url       The smb url to get information for
 *
 * @param st        pointer to a buffer that will be filled with
 *                  standard Unix struct statvfs information.
 *
 * @return          0 on success, &lt; 0 on error with errno set:
 *                  - EBADF  filedes is bad.
 *                  - EACCES Permission denied.
 *                  - EBADF fd is not a valid file descriptor
 *                  - EINVAL Problems occurred in the underlying routines
 *		      or smbc_init not called.
 *                  - ENOMEM Out of memory
 *
 * @see             Unix fstatvfs()
 *
 */</doc>
